{"tid":994754,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"蘇民峰：2018 股樓回落 2019 股樓大旺","createTime":"2019-01-25T02:38:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T04:28:49.000Z","uid":99885,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"665aea07bde402dac015858df1cab6828ce7616c","tid":994754,"uid":99885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T02:38:09.000Z","msg":"【狗年運程】蘇民峰：股市宜轉攻為守，樓舖無投資價值<br />\n<br />\n狗年預測重點︰<br />\n　<br />\n　‧股樓回落機會大<br />\n　‧股市在2月4日或4月5日回落後，跌至年底回升<br />\n　‧屬木（如服裝、木材、藥材等）、屬火（如石油、電訊、科網等）股票有得升<br />\n　‧2019年至2021年全港經濟活躍，股樓大旺<br />\n　<br />\n股市篇：大市先低後高 保本為上<br />\n　<br />\n　　踏入2018年，每逢開市日的早上，電話不時傳來「恒指再破頂」的信息，股民正冀望35000點來臨之際，蘇民峰預測今年大市先跌後升，但觀乎現況似乎有所出入，「舊年本來我睇（全年最高位是）11月7日，點知去到11月22日先到頂（當日最高報30003點），舊年遲咗，今年咪又會有機會遲咗，1月是應該跌的，點知而家繼續升。」而他去年預測1月6日後、5月6日後的低位，則未有出現，全年最低位為1月3日的開市日。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/mobile/tc/news/topic_news_detail.php?category=special&amp;newsid=8387\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftc%2Fnews%2Ftopic_news_detail.php%3Fcategory%3Dspecial%26newsid%3D8387&d=7Gg4yc1GkjEDi0YnFurNPf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=e1199711\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/mobile/tc/news/topic_news_detail.php?category=special&amp;newsid=8387</a>"},{"pid":"d3c8ea72e8cd53ec993bf32ef5734e49f74dd11c","tid":994754,"uid":60057,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T02:47:01.000Z","msg":"有冇人其實可以搵返呢班神棍上年年頭講過D咩野，一對比就知係咪有料到"},{"pid":"faf61b9c7ec3f9a8f89a377ee8044c90347d4740","tid":994754,"uid":102198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T04:13:01.000Z","msg":"gun!"},{"pid":"cdd2e54261cb19527c6274203d563ed6847a6978","tid":994754,"uid":131064,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T04:14:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">估中左WO</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"eb530c659cdc13d99b022d2f1498735d84affc93","tid":994754,"uid":159876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T04:14:48.000Z","msg":"神算"},{"pid":"77b7666826b0f8fe4a220b4d2dd53e597d8f3d61","tid":994754,"uid":223525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T04:19:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一擊即中"},{"pid":"7245e2a8fc9cd17c957ab600ef1215a6c2d1e109","tid":994754,"uid":162906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T04:28:49.000Z","msg":"科網等股票有得升"}]}